text: Hey Millie. I made a little video to introduce myself that I'm going to try to send on here.

Don't worry about responding with a video. It would be great to hear a little about you, but you can use this chat or video/audio to do that, whatever way you prefer. We can also just set a time to chat and you can tell me more at that time if you prefer. I hear you are interested in photography! I like photography too.

Thank you for contacting me, I really appreciate your time. I'm sorry it has taken so long to respond unfortunately I've been have troubles with my internet but I hope they're sorted now. I am very interested in photography! All things creative really :relaxed:

Sweet! That's very cool, I am also interested in all things creative too :) No worries about any delays, troubles with the internet affect us all haha, not much you can do about that! The video I made might be really heavy in terms if file size, so if you are having internet troubles that might be a pain for you to download. Let me know if you can't watch it and I'll send a more compressed version

I managed to watch your video it made things a lot more personal :grin: if my internet allows I would be happy to send one back :grin: I was very impressed to hear you worked on such an amazing film! I would love to hear more about it. A job in acting and film industry has always interested me.

Glad to hear that! I wasn't even thinking about how there were jobs in the film industry at your age haha, so you are way ahead of me already ;p Gravity was a lot of fun to work on. It was the first feature film I worked on, so that made it particularly exciting. :crossed_fingers:  you're internet comes back!
